### Configure Tracing Options (Screenshots, Snapshots, Sources, Title)

Source: https://github.com/microsoft/playwright/blob/main/docs/src/api/class-tracing.md

Configure Playwright tracing options to capture screenshots, DOM snapshots, source files, and set a custom trace title. Screenshots and snapshots aid in timeline preview and network activity recording. Source files can be included for JavaScript, C#, Python, and Java, with specific environment variable requirements for Java.

```javascript
await context.tracing.start({ screenshots: true, snapshots: true, sources: true, title: 'My Trace Title' });
```

```csharp
await context.Tracing.StartAsync(new() {
  Screenshots = true,
  Snapshots = true,
  Sources = true,
  Title = "My Trace Title"
});
```

